"ECLIMD Options ==========================

"if has('netbeans_enabled')
:set guioptions-=m "turn off menu bar
:set guioptions-=T "turn off toolbar

":set guioptions-=L "turn off left scrollbar
":set guioptions-=l

" Disable updating history of files
:let g:EclimProjectKeepLocalHistory = 0

" Open searches in new tab:
:let g:EclimDefaultFileOpenAction = 'tabnew'

"Eclim Code Completion remap:
:inoremap <C-h> <C-x><C-u>

"VICTORY! Ctrl+PageUp/PageDown functionality
:nmap <silent> <C-PageUp> :call eclim#vimplugin#FeedKeys('Ctrl+PageUp')<cr>
:nmap <silent> <C-PageDown> :call eclim#vimplugin#FeedKeys('Ctrl+PageDown')<cr>

"Map Ctrl+Shift+B to set new breakpoint
:nmap <C-d> :call eclim#vimplugin#FeedKeys('Ctrl+Shift+B')<cr>

"endif

"============================= ECLIMD Options
